---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: About WPCNA
metaDescription: Learn what WPCNA is and how it connects neighborhoods across White Plains.
---
{% from "components/macros.njk" import resourceCard %}

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>About WPCNA</h1>
    <p>The White Plains Council of Neighborhood Associations brings together neighborhood groups from across the city.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <article class="about-copy">
        <p><strong>WPCNA</strong> is a volunteer council made up of representatives from neighborhood associations throughout White Plains. It serves as a forum for sharing information, raising concerns, and keeping communication open between neighborhoods and the broader community.</p>

        <p>Each neighborhood has its own character, concerns, and priorities. WPCNA exists to help those neighborhoods stay connected to each other, to the city, and to what is happening across White Plains.</p>

        <p>This site is part of that effort. It brings together civic events, meeting agendas, neighborhood information, and community resources in one place — organized with a neighborhood lens so residents can find what matters to them.</p>

        <p>White Plains is the county seat of Westchester and a growing city with a busy downtown, a Metro-North connection to Grand Central, and a wide range of residential neighborhoods. The city carries the energy and diversity you would expect from a place with strong connections to both Westchester County and New York City.</p>

        <p>If you are looking to get a better sense of what is happening in White Plains, or want to get more involved in your neighborhood, you are in the right place.</p>
      </article>

      <div>
        <figure class="about-photo">
          <img src="{{ site.aboutImage | withPrefix }}" alt="{{ site.aboutImageAlt }}" loading="lazy">
        </figure>

        <div class="sidebar-card" id="contact-form">
          <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
          <h3>Get in touch</h3>
          <p>Questions, updates, or neighborhood news can be sent here.</p>
          <form class="contact-form" action="{{ site.contactFormAction }}" method="POST">
            {% if site.contactFormCc %}<input type="hidden" name="_cc" value="{{ site.contactFormCc }}">{% endif %}
            <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="{{ site.contactFormSubject }}">
            <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false">
            <input type="hidden" name="_template" value="table">

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="contact-name">Name</label>
              <input id="contact-name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="contact-email">Email</label>
              <input id="contact-email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="contact-subject">Subject</label>
              <input id="contact-subject" name="topic" type="text" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="contact-message">Message</label>
              <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" type="submit">Send message</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="spotlight">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Get Involved</p>
        <h2>Attend a meeting</h2>
        <p>{{ site.meetingNote }}</p>
        <p>Meetings are open to anyone interested in civic life in White Plains. When in person, we meet at:</p>
        <address style="font-style:normal;margin:0.5rem 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.5">
          <strong>White Plains Board of Education</strong><br>
          5 Homeside Lane<br>
          White Plains, NY 10605<br>
          <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=White+Plains+Board+of+Education+5+Homeside+Lane+White+Plains+NY" rel="external noopener">View on Google Maps &rarr;</a>
        </address>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--ink-muted)">Confirm the format (in person or Zoom) on the latest agenda before heading over.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="spotlight-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Explore</p>
        <h3>See what's happening</h3>
        <p>Browse upcoming events, explore neighborhoods, or check out the quick links on the home page.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-block" href="{{ '/events/' | withPrefix }}" style="margin-top:0.75rem">What's happening</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
